      "text": "Inspect brake hoses/pipes"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. Brake hose/pipe Inspection"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "1",
      "text": "Inspect brake hoses for damage, interference with other parts, kinks, or leaks. Inspect brake pipes for crushed, bent, damaged, corroded, or leaking fluid. Inspect hose and pipe joints for oozing or leakage, and retighten as necessary to the specified torque."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "number": "4",
      "text": "Inspect the joint between the VSA modulator control unit and the pipe for oozing or leakage, and retighten to the specified torque if necessary."
    },
